16 Roadmap
**********

All eight items deferred past the v0.1.0 tag landed in v0.2.0:

   • Auto-refresh of ‘*Pending*’ on registry mutation
     (‘pending-list-auto-refresh’ defcustom).
   • Pulse-on-resolve flash via ‘pulse.el’ (‘pending-pulse-on-resolve’
     defcustom).
   • ‘pending-as-promise’ adapter for ‘aio’ users (optional add-on
     ‘pending-aio.el’).
   • SVG spinner for graphical frames (‘pending-svg-spinner-enable’ /
     ‘pending-svg-spinner-size’ defcustoms).
   • Fringe bitmap indicator beside the placeholder
     (‘pending-fringe-bitmap’ defcustom).
   • ‘*Region Lock*’-style description buffer for a single placeholder
     (‘pending-describe’ command and ‘pending-description-mode’).
   • Indirect-buffer projection of read-only properties
     (‘pending-protect-adopted-region’ defcustom).
   • ‘pending-test--with-mocked-time’ macro for deterministic
     fast-forward testing.

   Still on the roadmap after v0.2:

   • Group operations (‘pending-cancel-group’).


